text: This is probably one of the defining features about me and the way that I trade compared to other people is that I am the same idiot and degenerate as everybody else out here. It literally, I'm just a random dude now on the internet, but I am straight up like everybody else. But the difference is what I started to do was this work that people don't like to do. But what it enables me to do is understand definitively what makes the most sense out of the different variables that can be tied into any individual trade or any individual strategy and then I can optimize off of those. That is the purpose of this.
